text: Falsimohnia is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Falsimohnia include: * Falsimohnia albozonata (Watson, 1886) * Falsimohnia anderssoni (Strebel, 1908) * Falsimohnia fulvicans (Strebel, 1908) * Falsimohnia hoshiaii (Numanami, 1996) * Falsimohnia innocens (E. A. Smith, 1907) * Falsimohnia minor (Strebel, 1908) * Falsimohnia okutanii (Numanami, 1996) ==References== ==External links== Category:Gastropod genera
title: Falsimohnia
